# 🌐 My Web Application Template

**A reusable PHP web application template with basic structure for quick project setup**

---

## 🧩 Template Features
- 🏗️ Pre-built project structure
- ♻️ Reusable components
- 📱 Responsive-ready
- 🔄 Easy to extend

---

## 🛠️ Technical Stack
- **Core:** PHP 8.0+
- **Frontend:** HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript (ES6)
- **Database:** MySQL (PDO)
- **Dependencies:** 
  - Bootstrap 5 (for quick styling)
  - Font Awesome (icons)

---

## 🗂️ Project Structure

my-webapp/
├── assets/
│ ├── css/ # Stylesheets
│ ├── js/ # JavaScript files
│ └── images/ # All media assets
├── includes/
│ ├── config.php # Database configuration
│ ├── header.php # Common header
│ ├── footer.php # Common footer
│ └── functions.php # Global functions
├── pages/ # All application pages
│ ├── home.php
│ ├── about.php
│ └── contact.php
├── index.php # Main entry point
└── README.md # This documentation


---

## 🚀 Quick Start

### Requirements
- PHP 8.0 or higher
- MySQL 5.7+ (if using database)
- Apache/Nginx web server

